    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台招商管理规则》及其关联规则的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1284827650648576000",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为营造良好的营商环境，提升商家综合运营体验，我们将对店铺类型进行全面简化，取消POP原店铺类型中的卖场店。如有多品牌经营需求可以选择入驻到专营店；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">已开通卖场店的商家，平台会依据经营情况统一将店铺类型调整为专营店(相关规则以专营店为准)。商家也可自行申请店铺类型的变更。同时针对《&ldquo;京东JD.COM&rdquo;开放平台在线服务协议&nbsp;》进行修订公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东将陆续对引用卖场店的其他关联规则作出相应调整，调整后的规则替代前述关联规则并生效，关联规则主要调整点如下表所示。</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"margin-left: 4.65pt; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 260.25pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"347\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">主要调整点</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 309.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"413\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整后</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 260.25pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"347\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卖场店店铺类型的相关描述</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 309.75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"413\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 260.25pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"347\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">《&ldquo;京东JD.COM&rdquo;开放平台在线服务协议&nbsp;》争议解决方式进行变更</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 309.75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"413\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">由宿迁仲裁委员会进行仲裁</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本次变更于&nbsp;2025&nbsp;年9月15日公示，于9月22日正式生效。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">申请店铺类型变更操作路径：</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在京麦后台依次点击店铺管理一店铺信息一店铺名称后的修改按钮，按系统提示操作，并准备相应资质材料。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
